org.eclipse.papyrus.MARTE.MARTE_DesignModel.SRM.SW_Concurrency

Interface SwConcurrentResource

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Resource, SwResource
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Alarm, InterruptResource, SwSchedulableResource
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AlarmImpl, InterruptResourceImpl, SwConcurrentResourceImpl, SwSchedulableResourceImpl

    public interface SwConcurrentResource
extends SwResource
    A representation of the model object 'Sw Concurrent Resource'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Type
    • Activation Capacity
    • Entry Points
    • Adress Space
    • Period Elements
    • Priority Elements
    • Stack Size Elements
    • Activate Services
    • Enable Concurrency Services
    • Resume Services
    • Suspend Services
    • Terminate Services
    • Disable Concurrency Services
    • Share Data Resources
    • Message Resources
    • Mutual Exclusion Resources
    • Notification Resources
    • Heap Size Elements

    See Also:
    SW_ConcurrencyPackage.getSwConcurrentResource()
